text: This was a new event in the ITF Women's Circuit. American-duo Shelby Rogers and Coco Vandeweghe won the title, defeating the top seeds Jocelyn Rae and Anna Smith in the final, 7–5, 7–6(7–1). == Seeds == == Draw == == References == * Draw Aegon Eastbourne Trophy - Doubles
